22:52.080 --> 22:53.873
<i>He's an older man, yes.</i>

22:53.957 --> 22:57.293
'Cause I've got two old men here.
Is he the fat one?

22:58.169 --> 23:01.881
<i>You do realise that Clayton Harding
is a personal friend of mine?</i>

23:01.965 --> 23:03.716
- What's that got to do with anything?
<i>- Right.</i>

23:03.800 --> 23:05.134
(HANGS UP PHONE)

23:08.137 --> 23:09.389
(SIGHS)

23:16.020 --> 23:17.313
(REDIALS)

23:18.147 --> 23:21.317
<i>- WOMAN: Parsons Gallery.</i>
- Is he the one with the wonky eye, then?

23:21.442 --> 23:22.819
