28:27.874 --> 28:30.167
- Sexually-attractive women.
- Do you mind?

28:30.251 --> 28:31.502
What?

28:31.586 --> 28:33.462
- Hey, Lawrence, how are you?
- Hey, I'm good.

28:33.546 --> 28:35.298
Good to see you.

28:35.381 --> 28:36.382
Look at that.

28:36.465 --> 28:38.384
All night long, people have been
treating us like royalty.

28:38.467 --> 28:39.719
In London, the journalist's motto is,

28:39.802 --> 28:41.512
"Everybody hates us,
and we don't care."

28:41.596 --> 28:44.432
Well, now you're one of the high priests
of what's hot and what's not.

28:44.515 --> 28:47.226
I shouldn't even be here.
I get thrown out of places like this.

28:47.310 --> 28:48.311
(CHUCKLES)

28:49.604 --> 28:51.397
(PHONE RINGING)

29:00.823 --> 29:03.242
Lawrence Maddox? Oh, my goodness.

29:03.701 --> 29:05.620
- Long time.
- Yeah.

29:06.078 --> 29:08.789
You know, it is so funny
I should run into you.

