29:13.169 --> 29:14.879
- It's low-budget. First-time director.
- Yeah.

29:14.962 --> 29:16.839
But it's really moving.

29:17.673 --> 29:20.635
Hey, you know,
maybe you could do a little...

29:21.260 --> 29:22.303
Vincent.

29:22.386 --> 29:24.597
- Good to see you.
- Lawrence, right?

29:24.680 --> 29:26.599
- Yeah.
- How are you, sir?

29:26.682 --> 29:27.934
- Good.
- Good to see you, too.

29:28.017 --> 29:30.186
- How's the picture?
- Pretty close to perfect,

29:30.269 --> 29:32.897
if I can just get all the experts
to leave me alone.

29:32.980 --> 29:34.690
In fact, I'm going to have
some screenings next week.

29:34.774 --> 29:36.525
- You should come by.
- Hey,

29:37.109 --> 29:40.446
that was Rachel Petkoff.
She's a fantastic actress.

29:40.529 --> 29:42.949
