30:20.027 --> 30:21.487
you've been in.

30:21.570 --> 30:23.155
Those episodes of <i>The Love Boat</i>

30:23.239 --> 30:26.158
and <i>The Bionic Woman</i> and <i>Song Birds.</i>

30:26.659 --> 30:30.621
<i>In The Night.</i> And I saw
