30:30.705 --> 30:32.665
<i>The Twilight Zone,</i> "House of Mirrors."

30:32.748 --> 30:34.041
(BOTH LAUGH)

30:34.125 --> 30:35.251
Right!

30:35.334 --> 30:38.671
