has to be <i>A Day Too Long.</i>

30:38.754 --> 30:40.381
You were great in that.

30:46.387 --> 30:49.765
- What's your name, honey?
- It's Sidney. Sidney Young.

30:50.516 --> 30:53.227
Sidney Young.

30:56.313 --> 30:58.482
- Thanks.
- I'll remember that.

31:00.860 --> 31:02.403
Thank you.

31:05.239 --> 31:08.909
I mean, you look around you
and it's all shit, you know.

31:08.993 --> 31:10.828
No one's making movies
that are fucking worthwhile.

31:10.911 --> 31:13.164
I have to disagree with you, Vincent.

31:13.539 --> 31:15.875
You're making movies
that are worthwhile.

31:15.958 --> 31:18.961
This is what I'm saying, you know.
You have to inspire yourself.

31:19.045 --> 31:21.630
I am my role model. I want to be me.

31:22.548 --> 31:24.800
- What's the greatest film ever made?
- Excuse me?

31:24.884 --> 31:27.720
What is the greatest film ever made?
Have a guess.

31:28.220 --> 31:31.974
Well, I don't know.
I don't think there is one...

31:32.058 --> 31:33.517
- Have a guess.
- Yeah. No. Have a guess.

31:33.601 --> 31:35.186
What's the greatest film ever made?

31:35.269 --> 31:38.439
It's hard to say.
I mean, I personally love <i>La Dolce Vita.</i>

31:38.522 --> 31:39.565
