32:25.861 --> 32:30.282
- What are you? A publicist?
- I don't really like that word, Sidney.

32:30.825 --> 32:32.701
What do I call you, then?

32:33.702 --> 32:35.830
You can call me Eleanor.

32:36.539 --> 32:38.124
All right.

32:38.541 --> 32:40.000
There she is.

32:41.877 --> 32:42.878
(MOUTHS)

33:34.555 --> 33:36.265
