36:40.991 --> 36:42.618
MADDOX: Great coverage.

36:45.913 --> 36:47.456
From Sophie Maes.

36:50.626 --> 36:53.462
"Thanks for the great night." Sweet kid.

36:54.880 --> 36:57.091
Sidney, about last night.

36:58.008 --> 37:01.303
A word of advice.
Don't talk to the celebrities.

37:02.554 --> 37:05.265
